Package rl.photoviewer.swing.view Description

Contains classes to create the Swing-based version of the photo viewer's view component. The main class is PVView. It defines the root object in the view and assembles the complete object structure of the view. All buttons and menu items use command strings defined in Commands as action commands to indicate their intend to the controller. The StatusPanel is responsible for error handling.
Author:
Ruediger Lunde
